{"tid":1342503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣入] TVB想spin成示威者追打市民 要正視聽","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:42:58.000Z","uid":199012,"like":196,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"02d4fc74137656d8430b65352fe452db36077477","tid":1342503,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"Tvb新聞完全冇話係示威完着黑衫返屋企嘅市民畀白衫黑社會打 淨係話暴力事件同埋發生打鬥 仲要播政府聲明咁一次過遣責晒上環同元朗 搞到好似係示威者打人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要文宣畀多啲人知真相 尤其中佬佢哋好反感黑社會<br />\n<br />\n文宣重點<br />\n1. 黑社會打無辜示威者同路人<br />\n2. 黑社會打老人、小童同大肚婆<br />\n3. 兩個軍裝警察睇住白衫打人之後走咗<br />\n4. 999 cut線<br />\n5. 警察接報30分鐘都未出現 出現之後睇住白衫打完人走<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯同懷疑黑社會合作, 同白衫黑社會握手搭膊頭[/red<br />\n<br />\n大家用多啲相 寫清楚啲元朗嘅起因經過 政府幾冇能 黑警偏頗 <br />\n[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同埋邊個先係真暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n求大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8060b0aa039a7b5a1dd36d5a89067485e8523461","tid":1342503,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"696af54474d69a0f604349963f4ea2bd7e113206","tid":1342503,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c9ac3500eb4ac5cb6a0988487528a0379214e0d","tid":1342503,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1917ad36eb60bf0306b89985c3db46f90375c418","tid":1342503,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣巴絲"},{"pid":"181360bb912d6180fd95cdd2df8ec24fa69c7546","tid":1342503,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T